          "slidetitle": "Mitigating AI Supply Chain Risks",
          "subtitle": "Strategies to reduce and manage exposure",
          "slidecontent": "• Start with pilot programmes in low-risk areas before scaling AI across the full supply chain\n• Maintain human oversight at critical decision points\n• Diversify suppliers to reduce dependence on AI-driven single-source procurement\n• Regularly audit AI outputs for accuracy and bias\n• Build contingency plans for system failures or unexpected forecast errors\n• Train staff to understand and challenge AI recommendations, not just accept them"
